    BarLineScatterCandleBubbleDataProvider, ChartInterface, ScatterDataProvider

    public class ScatterChart
extends BarLineChartBase<ScatterData>
implements ScatterDataProvider
    The ScatterChart. Draws dots, triangles, squares and custom shapes into the Chart-View. CIRCLE and SCQUARE offer the best performance, TRIANGLE has the worst performance.
